{
  "texts": [
    "We find 14 such discontinued tags: \"adaporg\", \"alg-geom\", \"chao-dyn\", \"cmp-lg\", \"comp-gas\", \"solv-int\", \"dg-ga\", \"patt-sol\", \"funct-an\", \"q-alg\", \"bayes-an\", \"acc-phys\", \"ao-sci\" and \"mtrl-th\".",
    "These tags constitute a minor portion of our dataset, with 7762 articles featuring at least one of them, accounting for 0.53% of the total articles analyzed.",
    "The impacted articles always contain at least one other tag that has not been discontinued.",
    "We therefore expect these changes to have a negligible impact on our primary findings.",
    "Low dimensional embeddingsTo reduce the dimensionality of the initial 175-dimensional field space, we use the tSNE algorithm, an unsupervised, parametric dimensionality reduction technique that retains the local data structure in the latent space [49,50]."
  ]
}